<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0d0d0f;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .mascot-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .mascot-img {
            max-height: 250px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2));
            animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #444 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            opacity: 0.1;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            z-index: -1;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .btn-home {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #0072ff 100%);
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 114, 255, 0.4);
            color: white;
        }

        @keyframes float {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Decorative Background Elements */
        .bg-glow {
            position: absolute;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 114, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            z-index: -2;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="bg-glow"></div>

    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="mascot-wrapper">
            <div class="error-code">404</div>
            <img src="/assets/what-rocky.png" alt="Mascot" class="mascot-img">
        </div>

        <h1>Hopa! Te-ai rătăcit?</h1>
        <p>Pagina pe care o cauți s-a ascuns mai bine decât Rocky în liniile noastre de cod. Hai să te ducem înapoi în
            siguranță.</p>

        <a href="/" class="btn-home">
            <i class="bi bi-house-door-fill"></i> Înapoi la Dashboard
        </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>